<H2><A NAME=SECTION00135300000000000000> Scale Operation</A></H2>
<P>
	<A NAME=est-scale HREF="est-scalebig.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="" SRC="est-scale.gif"></A>
	<A HREF="est-scalebig.gif">Figure (est-scale): Torus Scale Increased</A>
<P>
<tt>mged&gt; <em>Select the ``Scale'' entry in the solid edit menu</em> <BR>mged&gt; <em>p 1.5</em> <BR>mged&gt; 
</tt>
<P>
The vertex remains the same and all distances from the vertex are
multiplied by 1.5, the value entered with p.  See 
	<A HREF="est-scalebig.gif">Figure (est-scale)</A>
.
To return to the original scale, enter
<P>
<tt>mged&gt; <em>p 1</em> <BR>mged&gt; 
</tt>
<P>
